articles.title: Cyclone Freddy: Winds and rain lash Mozambique as storm arrives - BBC
articles.description: Freddy, which has caused at least 28 deaths over a month, has hit mainland Africa for a second time.
articles.content:
Mozambique is being lashed by rain, powerful winds and flooding as Cyclone Freddy makes landfall for the second time in a month.
